        <h1 class="zh-text" style="display: block;">大众汽车集团中国 - 业务变革组织评估框架</h1>
        <h1 class="en-text" style="display: none;">Volkswagen Group China - Business Change Organizational Evaluation Framework</h1>

        <div class="section">
            <div class="section-title zh-text" style="display: block;">评估框架说明</div>
            <div class="section-title en-text" style="display: none;">Framework Description</div>
            
            <p class="zh-text" style="display: block;">本框架用于业务部门（BU）自评因业务需求变化带来的组织变革需求，包括岗位配置必要性、数量合理性、层级设置及协同接口设计等。评估结果将作为HR COE介入的先行判断标准。</p>
            <p class="en-text" style="display: none;">This framework enables Business Units (BUs) to self-assess organizational change needs arising from business demand changes, including position necessity, quantity rationality, level setting, and collaboration interface design. Results serve as a preliminary screening criterion for HR COE intervention.</p>
            
            <div class="threshold-note">
                <p class="zh-text" style="display: block;"><strong>评分阈值说明：</strong><br>
                - 优先处理：总分≥80分，且无模块得分＜15分<br>
                - 需优化后重提：60-79分<br>
                - 不予受理：＜60分（变革需求不合理）</p>
                <p class="en-text" style="display: none;"><strong>Scoring Thresholds：</strong><br>
                - Priority Handling：Total score ≥80 points, no module score &lt;15<br>
                - Optimization Required：60-79 points (revision needed)<br>
                - Rejection：&lt;60 points (unnecessary change)</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Module 1: Business Change Legitimacy -->
        <div class="module">
            <div class="module-title zh-text" style="display: block;">模块一：业务变革合法性评估（总分26分）</div>
            <div class="module-title en-text" style="display: none;">Module 1: Business Change Legitimacy (26 points)</div>
            
            <div class="criteria-group">
                <div class="criteria-title zh-text" style="display: block;">1. 变革驱动因素（10分）</div>
                <div class="criteria-title en-text" style="display: none;">1. Change Drivers (10 points)</div>
                
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="zh-text" style="display: block;">请选择变革驱动类型（可多选）：</label>
                    <label class="en-text" style="display: none;">Select change driver types (multiple selection allowed)：</label>
                    <select id="driver-type" multiple="">
                        <option value="strategy" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">战略调整（如电动化、智能网联业务拓展）</option>
                        <option value="strategy" class="en-text" style="display: none;">Strategic Adjustment (e.g., electrification, intelligent connectivity expansion)</option>
                        <option value="regulation" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">合规要求（如新能源汽车安全法规更新）</option>
                        <option value="regulation" class="en-text" style="display: none;">Regulatory Compliance (e.g., NEV safety regulation updates)</option>
                        <option value="market" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">市场需求（如用户对智能座舱功能需求增长）</option>
                        <option value="market" class="en-text" style="display: none;">Market Demand (e.g., growing user demand for smart cockpit features)</option>
                        <option value="efficiency" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">效率提升（如跨区域业务协同优化）</option>
                        <option value="efficiency" class="en-text" style="display: none;">Efficiency Improvement (e.g., cross-regional collaboration optimization)</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="zh-text" style="display: block;">请简述变革与集团战略的关联性：</label>
                    <label class="en-text" style="display: none;">Briefly describe alignment with group strategy：</label>
                    <textarea id="strategy-alignment" placeholder="zh: 例如：本变革响应集团&#39;2030 NEW AUTO&#39;战略中的智能驾驶技术研发需求...
en: e.g., This change responds to R&amp;D needs for intelligent driving technology in the Group&#39;s &#39;2030 NEW AUTO&#39; strategy..."></textarea>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="criteria-group">
                <div class="criteria-title zh-text" style="display: block;">2. 影响范围（8分）</div>
                <div class="criteria-title en-text" style="display: none;">2. Impact Scope (8 points)</div>
                
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="zh-text" style="display: block;">变革影响范围：</label>
                    <label class="en-text" style="display: none;">Change impact scope：</label>
                    <select id="impact-scope">
                        <option value="single" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">单一团队</option>
                        <option value="single" class="en-text" style="display: none;">Single Team</option>
                        <option value="cross-team" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">跨团队</option>
                        <option value="cross-team" class="en-text" style="display: none;">Cross-Team</option>
                        <option value="bu" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">整个BU</option>
                        <option value="bu" class="en-text" style="display: none;">Entire BU</option>
                        <option value="group" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">集团层面</option>
                        <option value="group" class="en-text" style="display: none;">Group Level</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="criteria-group">
                <div class="criteria-title zh-text" style="display: block;">3. 实施紧迫性（8分）</div>
                <div class="criteria-title en-text" style="display: none;">3. Implementation Urgency (8 points)</div>
                
                <div class="input-group">
                    <label class="zh-text" style="display: block;">计划实施时间：</label>
                    <label class="en-text" style="display: none;">Planned implementation timeline：</label>
                    <select id="urgency">
                        <option value="high" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">≤3个月（高紧急）</option>
                        <option value="high" class="en-text" style="display: none;">≤3 months (High Urgency)</option>
                        <option value="medium" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">3-6个月（中紧急）</option>
                        <option value="medium" class="en-text" style="display: none;">3-6 months (Medium Urgency)</option>
                        <option value="low" class="zh-text" style="display: block;">＞6个月（低紧急）</option>
                        <option value="low" class="en-text" style="display: none;">＞6 months (Low Urgency)</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
